body:
@mulhearn @mandrenguyen 
This PR is meant to go on top of #12364 , and disables the manual override of the HI Stage1 Level-1 trigger parameters since we expect to get the real information from the GT.

@mulhearn suggests that we wait for the GT to actually be made before merging this, but I am of the opinion that we should just go ahead and do it so that we don't need to wait for a PR merge and new release when the new GT is made. Comments welcome.
